<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Tuxedo Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood of Tuxedo Park was, and still is, one of the most vibrant and sought-after locations of Calgary with a population of 5,000 residents! Tuxedo Park has a lot of facilities and is one of the best places in Calgary for a real estate investment.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Since it is an urban neighborhood, its proximity to the downtown area and its numerous facilities, Tuxedo Park is not only suitable for families, but for business people, students and others as well.</p>

        </div>
